d_m: so, when i had a jukebox set up, i had a "play once" queue
d_m: so stuff there played once but went away. it owuldn't repeat
d_m: and if the queue was empty it would fall back to a "primary" playlist and choose random songs (but not totally random, it avoided repeating a song)
d_m: so you could have a general vibe going but if someone wanted to hear something they could queue it up
d_m: and if someone wanted to "DJ" then they'd queue up like 5 songs or whatever
d_m: but once the queue was empty it would go back to "random play" mode
