wolfdog: shortly before going to bed i realized why my client was really freezing
wolfdog: the channel i am using for sending events client->server wasn't buffered
wolfdog: so if two events happened at the same time (i.e. send message + poll), the UI would freeze waiting for the first event to be handled, and the comm thread would freeze waiting
wolfdog: the moral of the story is that concurrency is Hard
