jukebox: playlist [NAME] : Add premade playlist to queue
jukebox: skip            : Skips current song
jukebox: p               : Pause/Resume
jukebox: seek				: Go to end of queue and play last song
jukebox: queue				: Show songs in queue
jukebox: song            : See current song
jukebox: clear				: Clears the queue, might cause some clients to disconnect
jukebox: add [URL]       : Add a audiostream URL to the queue
jukebox: info            : See how to connect to the stream
jukebox: list            : List pre-made playlists (there are some secret ones)
